---
title: Smart Creamy Honey-Mustard Pork with Sheet Pan Veggie Medley
description: No need to sacrifice flavour when opting to be more carb-conscious with this recipe! A healthy serving of veggies are roasted until golden- brown and served with tender pork and a creamy honey-mustard sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/porc-et-sauce-cremeuse-a-la-moutarde-au-miel-261b5e9e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/smart-creamy-honey-mustard-pork-64d1eaf9eabf7cbec70f721b-b7d11c84.pdf
